"""AutoLogin — magic-link tokens for the tests-360 pattern.

ONLY generated when ``module-autologin-tests360`` is selected. Token redemption
is POST-only; optional GET confirmation pages render CSRF-protected forms and
never create sessions directly.

The token endpoint REQUIRES a valid signed token in the URL; without it
the view 404s. Without the module active, no such endpoint exists at all.

Anti-pattern avoided (inpacto-ghl-integrations audit): GET requests never
start a session. POST redemption requires the signed token and marks it used
atomically.
"""

default_app_config = "apps.accounts.autologin.apps.AutoLoginConfig"
